FBIS4-36634 "drnes113_n_94014" FBIS-NES-94-113 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 LEBANON Nasrallah Pledges Continued Resistance Nasrallah Pledges Continued Resistance NC1306072994 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0430 GMT 13 Jun 94 NC1306072994 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] Hizballah Secretary General Hasan Nasrallah has pledged to continue the jihad and resistance and not to capitulate regardless of Israeli reactions. He called for putting internal differences aside at this stage, adding that civic peace must be protected. He said: We do not advocate any form of indigenous security and we are not the security alternative for anyone.
